SingletonTaskFactoryLoader - Class in provided.client.model.taskUtils
An implementation of ITaskFactoryLoader that loads ITaskFactory instances defined by a singleton object in a static field of the desired ITask class called "FACTORY".

If this loader attempts to load a non-existent ITask class, an internally-defined ErrorTask instance will be returned.
